Indications for preoperative laparoscopic ultrasonography. 109 laparoscopic ultrasound examinations are performed for a period of 7 years (1993-1999). Laparoscope R. Wolf and 7.5 MHz linear probe "Aloka" are used. On the basis of the results analysis the following indications for laparoscopic ultrasonography (LUS) are recommended: 1. Uncertain diagnosis 2. Contradictory results of imaging technics